#

Spiced Turmeric Chicken with Coconut Jasmine Rice and Mango Salsa

$20
600 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

ChickenTropicalSpicyComfort Food

Description

A vibrant dish featuring succulent turmeric-spiced chicken paired with fragrant coconut jasmine rice and fresh mango salsa for a tropical twist.

Ingredients

  • Chicken thighs: 4 pieces
  • Turmeric powder: 2 teaspoons
  • Cumin powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • Garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: 1 teaspoon
  • Black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Coconut milk: 1 cup
  • Jasmine rice: 1 cup
  • Mango: 1, diced
  • Red onion: 1/4, finely chopped
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Red bell pepper: 1, diced
